heading: Defiled Catacomb Dungeon Guide
content: Defiled Catacomb long linear dungeon with good monsters, and home of the disappointing . Overall the length doesn't make this one of the best dungeons for grinding, but it still offers excellent clear times for builds that excel at Area of Effect damage for the Spiders and Skeleton families. While every dungeon has a somewhat randomized layout, there are patterns to where objectives and bosses are located. This map will help you identify those layouts so you can complete dungeons faster and maximize your XP and loot per hour! Reviewed by
